Script,Gambling3N
setDealerCode(`

/*
convention-card: 21GF-Gambling
auction-filter: Auction.....\n3NT? +
*/

dealer south

# Gambling 3N
hcp(south)>8 and hcp(south)<12  // could have a Q or two J's outside
and
(
(top3(south,diamonds)==3 and diamonds(south)>6)
or
(top3(south,clubs)==3 and clubs(south)>6)
)
and shape(south,any 9xxx +any 8xxx +any 7xxx -any 4xxx -any 5xxx -any 6xxx)

`,"S",true)
Script
Button,Gambling 3N,\n\
--- Gambling 3N\n\
A gambling 3N opening bid shows a solid 7 or 8-card minor suit and less than a K outside.\n\
https://www.bridgebum.com/gambling_3nt.php\n\
%Gambling3N%
